b9=A.a(["Comprehensive FTA covering goods, services, investment, IP, digital trade","90%+ tariff elimination over 7-10 years phased timeline","Enhanced market access for Indian IT and pharma in EU","Binding sustainability and labor chapters included","EU is India's 3rd largest trading partner after USA and China"],b8)
