p=A.a(["India's first comprehensive CCTS \u2014 market-based emission reduction","BEE is administrator; trading on Indian Carbon Market (ICM)","Industries exceeding benchmarks earn Carbon Credit Certificates (CCCs)","Targets 45% emission intensity reduction by 2030 (from 2005)","Follows EU ETS model \u2014 China launched carbon market in 2021"],b8)
